_sText:
A little fy_snow looking layout but with more spots and tricks.

Each team starts with weapons on the ground that you can pick up. 
They're are ladders on each block to go to the top of the "buildings"
each side with one sniper on top. 

Hurry before the buy time passes, and
teleport to the buy room where CT's and T's can buy weapons and ammo
then teleport back to the center of the map.

Makes for fun gameplay.
